      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a nice luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface wear consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features functioning as expected. It's a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks and drives great.",
